      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into bite-sized pieces</p>",
